What you need to know:

Coutinho came off the bench midway through the second half with Villa trailing 2-0 after Bruno Fernandes's double for UnitedCoutinho then converted Ramsey's cross five minutes later to ensure Steven Gerrard's side made amends for their FA Cup third round exit at United on MondayThe Portugal playmaker's second goal was the kind of eye-catching finish that made his name when he arrived at United from Sporting Lisbon in January 2020